Class ArrayDS

  • java.lang.Object
    • ArrayDS

  • public class ArrayDS
extends java.lang.Object
    Primitive Array Data Structure takes randomly generated number and creates an array using bubble sort it sorts the array, then deletes an element which is chosen based on the sorting order, then inserts a new element of value 10
